 M http://src.chromium.org/viewvc/native_client/trunk/src/native_client/src/trusted/service_runtime/win/debug_exception_handler.c?r1=8249&amp;r2=8248&amp;pathrev=8249

Exception handling: Windows: Always continue from a breakpoint event

This simplifies the code to remove the x86-32-specific check.

This is in preparation for attaching the debug exception handler on
demand.  That will require that the injected breakpoint works when
NaCl's patch to KiUserExceptionDispatcher in NTDLL is applied.

